collection.name: MultiverseVM
collection.description:
Multiverse VM is a collection of 8000 NFTs living on the Ethereum blockchain.
Each MVM has randomly generated outgoing links to other simulations, and through [Xeno Infinity](https://opensea.io/collection/xenoinfinity), users can instantly integrate the NFTs they own to use as their web3 identity.
The multiverse virtual machine contains mysterious technology, scientists suggest it seems to have the ability to create new realities.
